item.description:
This is the code used in Rstudio to make a time series using the lahman data set.
# extracting the data&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;
query&lt;- &ldquo;SELECT yearID,HR FROM Batting WHERE playerID = &lsquo;ruthba01&rsquo;&rdquo;
result&lt;- sqldf(query)
# visualize the data&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-
ggplot()+ geom_line(data=result,aes(x=yearID,y=HR))+ geom_point(data=result,aes(x=yearID,y=HR))+ ggtitle(&ldquo;Ruth&rsquo;s homerun Totals Through the Years&rdquo;)+ xlab(&ldquo;year&rdquo;)+ ylab(&ldquo;homeruns&rdquo;)
